MODULEøø;  Rem --- SLIME TRAILS --ø;  Rem ø;  Rem (FROM THE MOVIE OF THE SAME NAME)ø;  Rem ø;  Rem THIS GAME REQUIRES TWO JOYSTICKS PLUGGED INTO CONNECTORSø;  Rem NUMBER 1 AND 2 (STICKS 0 AND 1)ø;ø;This game was translated directlyø;from BASIC XL to ACTION!, line byø;line.  Please forgive the non-ACTION!ø;format of the program, but it works,ø;and the translation only took aboutø;an hour.øøBYTE Score0,Score1,H0,V0,H1,V1,ø     Hmv0,Hmv1,Vmv0,Vmv1,Volume,ø     Bang0,Bang1,HS,VSøBYTE Attract=77øCARD Delay,Count,Move,TempoøøBYTE FUNC Hstick(BYTE n)ø  IF (Stick(n)&8)=0 THEN RETURN (1) FIø  IF (Stick(n)&4)=0 THEN RETURN (255) FIø  RETURN (0)øøBYTE FUNC Vstick(BYTE n)ø  IF (Stick(n)&1)=0 THEN RETURN (1) FIø  IF (Stick(n)&2)=0 THEN RETURN (255) FIø  RETURN (0)øøøøPROC MAIN()ø; init for new game !!!!øDO ; infinite loopøøScore0=0:Score1=0ø;  Rem ø;  Rem ø;  Rem ROUND INITIALIZATIONøøDO ; terminated by the UNTIL far belowøøGraphics(7)øøcolor=1 øPlot(0,0):Drawto(0,79) øDrawto(159,79):Drawto(159,0) øDrawto(0,0)øøøtempo=400øøPrintE("SCORE")øPrintE("PLAYER 1PLAYER 2")øPrintF("%U%U%E", Score0, Score1)øøH0=40:V0=40:H1=119:V1=40øHmv0=1:Vmv0=0:Hmv1=-1:Vmv1=0øøøcolor=2:Plot(H0,V0) øcolor=3:Plot(H1,V1)øø;  Rem START A ROUNDøøFor Count=50 To 150 Step 50øDOø   For Volume=0 To 15ø   DOø     Sound(0,Count,10,15-Volume)ø     For Delay=1 to 1000 DO ODø   ODøOD                øøIF Hstick(0) THEN Hmv0=Hstick(0) FIøIF Hstick(1) THEN Hmv1=Hstick(1) FIøøFOR Move = 0 TO 65535 STEP 4øDOøAttract=0øIF (Move&255)=0 AND TEMPO>50ø     THEN TEMPO= (TEMPO * 3)/4  FIø                ø; Rem SENSE AND MOVE PLAYER 0øø   HS=Hstick(0)ø   If HS<>0 AND Hmv0=0 Then ø    Hmv0=HS:Vmv0=0ø    FIøø   VS=Vstick(0)ø   If VS<>0 AND Vmv0=0 Then ø    Vmv0=VS:Hmv0=0ø    FIøø   H0=H0+Hmv0:V0=V0-Vmv0øø   Bang0=Locate(H0,V0)ø   If Bang0=0 THEN   ø      color=2:Plot(H0,V0)ø      FIøø; Rem SENSE AND MOVE PLAYER 1øø   HS=Hstick(1)ø   If HS<>0 AND Hmv1=0 Then ø    Hmv1=HS:Vmv1=0ø    FIøø   VS=Vstick(1)ø   If VS<>0 AND Vmv1=0 Then ø    Vmv1=VS:Hmv1=0ø    FIøø   H1=H1+Hmv1:V1=V1-Vmv1øø   Bang1=Locate(H1,V1)ø   If Bang1=0 THEN  ø      color=3:Plot(H1,V1)ø      FIøø   If Bang0=0 AND Bang1=0 THENø      For Volume=0 To 14 Step 2 ø        DOø        Sound(0,Move&255,10,14-Volume)ø        For Delay=1 to TEMPO  DO ODø        OD ø   ø;  Rem SOMEBODY GOT BANGEDø ø   Elseøø     IF Bang0<>0 AND Bang1<>0 THEN ø     ;  do nothing ø     ELSEø       IF Bang0 THEN Score1=Score1+1 FIø       IF Bang1 THEN Score0=Score0+1 FIøø       For Volume=0 TO 15ø         DOø         If Bang0 Then Setcolor(1,4,15-Volume) FIø         If Bang1 Then Setcolor(2,4,15-Volume) FIø         Sound(0,23,0,15-Volume)ø         For Delay=1 to 1000 DO ODø         OD       ø      FIø    EXITø    Fiøøø  ODø; Rem CHECK FOR END OF GAMEøø  UNTIL (Score0>=10 OR Score1>=10) ODøø  Graphics(2)øø  If (Score0<Score1) Then     ø    PrintDE(6,"PLAYER 2 WINS:")ø    PrintD(6,"    ") PrintBD(6,Score1)ø    PrintD(6," TO ") PrintBD(6,Score0)ø  Else       ø    PrintDE(6,"PLAYER 1 WINS:")ø    PrintD(6,"    ") PrintBD(6,Score0)ø    PrintD(6," TO ") PrintBD(6,Score1)ø  Fiøø; Rem END OF A GAMEøø  PrintE("PUSH JOYSTICK BUTTON TO PLAY AGAIN")øø; Rem WAIT FOR A BUTTON TO BE PUSHEDøø  WHILE (Strig(0)<>0 AND Strig(1)<>0) DO OD øøOD ; !!!! main loop !!!!øRETURNøø